Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:33.50,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}光明与黑暗 相随相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:37.44,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仿若珍珠 连成一串
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:41.45,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:45.90,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶然也好 自然也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:50.62,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终将化作期待的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:54.34,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:57.19,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始渐渐上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:01.20,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有伪装 亦无需试探
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:05.76,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做最真的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:09.74,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坚守信仰 不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:13.35,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想告诉你
