Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:09.06,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my power, future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:14.58,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情の名前なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:18.59,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言い出せばキリがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:22.20,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の目が叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:26.26,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本能で聞き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:26.85,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:28.11,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}付き纏う
